Package net.fathomsoft.nova.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandListener
    Class that is used to listen to Commands.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bounds
    Class used to store data about a start and end location.
    Command
    Class that is used to issue a command to the Operating System.
    FileUtils
    Utility methods for File operations, such as: reading, writing, and manipulating file extensions.
    Location
    Class that contains information for a line number and character offset.
    Patterns
    Utility class that contains a multitude of pre-compiled patterns used for searching through text for specific events.
    Regex
    Utility class will several Regular Expression helper methods.
    Stack<E>
    Class that emulates the actions of a Stack.
    StringUtils
    Class that contains methods used for finding data about a String.
    SyntaxUtils
    Class used for getting information about the Syntax of Nova.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    Bounds.EmptyBoundsModificationException
    Exception thrown when the final EMPTY bounds is attempted to be modified.
